<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Protokol o uvedení do prevádzky - Vaillant</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --vaillant-teal: #00897B;
            --border-color: #bbbbbb;
            --bg-gray: #f2f2f2;
        }

        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.4; 
            color: #333; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 20px; 
            background-color: #e0e0e0; 
        }

        /* Simulácia A4 papiera */
        .paper { 
            background: white; 
            width: 210mm; 
            min-height: 297mm; 
            padding: 15mm 20mm; 
            margin: 20px auto; 
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); 
            position: relative; 
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        header { 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
            align-items: center; 
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--vaillant-teal); 
            padding-bottom: 15px; 
            margin-bottom: 25px; 
        }

        .logo-text { 
            color: var(--vaillant-teal); 
            font-weight: 800; 
            font-size: 34px; 
            letter-spacing: -1.5px; 
            margin: 0;
        }

        .title-block { text-align: right; }
        h1 { 
            font-size: 20px; 
            margin: 0; 
            color: var(--vaillant-teal); 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        h2 { 
            font-size: 13px; 
            background: var(--vaillant-teal); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 8px 12px; 
            margin-top: 15px; 
            margin-bottom: 10px; 
            border-radius: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        table { 
            width: 100%; 
            border-collapse: collapse; 
            margin-bottom: 12px; 
            font-size: 12px; 
        }

        table, th, td { border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
        th, td { padding: 6px 10px; text-align: left; }
        th { background-color: var(--bg-gray); width: 28%; font-weight: 600; }

        /* Vstupné polia */
        input[type="text"], textarea {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px transparent;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: inherit;
            padding: 2px 4px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: rgba(0,137,123,0.02);
        }
        
        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vaillant-teal);
            background-color: white;
        }

        .checkbox-section { margin: 10px 0; font-size: 12px; }
        .check-item { 
            margin-bottom: 6px; 
            display: flex; 
            align-items: flex-start; 
            gap: 10px; 
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .footer-sig { 
            margin-top: 40px; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
            font-size: 11px; 
        }
        .sig-box { 
            border-top: 1px solid #333; 
            width: 42%; 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-top: 30px; 
            padding-top: 8px; 
        }

        /* Foto sekcia */
        .photo-container {
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: 1px dashed #ccc;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: 100px;
        }
        #photoPreview {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 350px;
            display: none;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* Ovládacie prvky */
        .controls {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-print { background: var(--vaillant-teal); }
        .btn-photo { background: #555; }

        @media print {
            body { background: white; padding: 0; }
            .paper { box-shadow: none; margin: 0; width: 100%; border: none; padding: 10mm; }
            .controls, .btn-photo-input { display: none !important; }
            input, textarea { border-bottom: none !important; background: transparent !important; padding: 0 !important; }
            input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder { color: transparent; }
            .photo-container { border: none !important; padding: 0 !important; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="controls">
    <button class="btn btn-print" onclick="window.print()">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9V2h12v7"></path><path d="M6 18H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><rect x="6" y="14" width="12" height="8"></rect></svg>
        Vytlačiť protokol
    </button>
    <label class="btn btn-photo">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"></circle><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"></polyline></svg>
        Vložiť fotku inštalácie
        <input type="file" id="fileInput" accept="image/*" style="display: none;" onchange="previewImage(event)">
    </label>
</div>

<div class="paper">
    <header>
        <div class="logo-container"><p class="logo-text">Vaillant</p></div>
        <div class="title-block">
            <h1>Protokol o uvedení do prevádzky</h1>
            <small style="color: #666;">Tepelné čerpadlo / Systémové riešenie</small>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Zákazník / Miesto inštalácie</th>
                <td>
                    Meno: <input type="text" placeholder="Doplniť meno zákazníka..."><br>
                    Adresa: <input type="text" placeholder="Doplniť adresu miesta inštalácie...">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Autorizovaný servis (VSP)</th>
                <td>
                    Firma: <strong>SPEKTRA INSTALL</strong><br>
                    Adresa: <strong>Hollého 210, 015 01 Rajec</strong><br>
                    IČO: <strong>53690036</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp; DIČ: <strong>2121459450</strong><br>
                    Technik: <strong>Pavol Pastorek</strong>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </section>

    <h2>1. Identifikácia zariadenia</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Vonkajšia jednotka</th>
            <td>Model: <input type="text" style="width: 150px;"> Sériové č.: <input type="text" style="width: 200px;"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Vnútorná jednotka / Modul</th>
            <td>Model: <input type="text" style="width: 150px;"> Sériové č.: <input type="text" style="width: 200px;"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Zásobník / Príslušenstvo</th>
            <td>Typ: <input type="text" style="width: 150px;"> Objem: <input type="text" style="width: 60px;"> litrov</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>2. Kvalita vody a hydraulické parametre (VDI 2035)</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td>Tvrdosť vody: <input type="text" style="width: 60px;"> °dH</td>
            <td>pH vody: <input type="text" style="width: 60px;"></td>
            <td>Magnetický filter: <input type="text" style="width: 80px;" placeholder="Áno / Nie"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Tlak systéme: <input type="text" style="width: 60px;"> bar</td>
            <td>Prietok: <input type="text" style="width: 60px;"> l/min</td>
            <td>Expanzia (predtlak): <input type="text" style="width: 60px;"> bar</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>3. Softvérová konfigurácia</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Vykurovacia krivka</th>
            <td><input type="text" style="width: 80px;"></td>
            <th>Bivalentný bod</th>
            <td><input type="text" style="width: 80px;"> °C</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Max. teplota výstupu</th>
            <td><input type="text" style="width: 80px;"> °C</td>
            <th>Doplnkový ohrev</th>
            <td><input type="text" style="width: 80px;"> kW</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>4. Fotodokumentácia inštalácie</h2>
    <div class="photo-container">
        <span id="photoPlaceholder" style="color: #999; font-style: italic;">Tu sa zobrazí nahratá fotografia (táto správa sa nevytlačí)</span>
        <img id="photoPreview" alt="Foto inštalácie">
    </div>

    <h2>5. Kontrola a odovzdanie</h2>
    <div class="checkbox-section">
        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" checked> Zariadenie pracuje bez aktívnych chybových hlásení.</label>
        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" checked> Vykonaná kontrola tesnosti spojov.</label>
        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" checked> Zákazník bol zaškolený do obsluhy regulátora.</label>
        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" checked> Dokumentácia a záručný list boli odovzdané.</label>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-sig">
        <div class="sig-box">Podpis a pečiatka technika (VSP)</div>
        <div class="sig-box">Podpis zákazníka / užívateľa</div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 10px; color: #888; border-top: 1px dashed #ddd; padding-top: 8px;">
        Dátum spustenia: <input type="text" style="width: 100px; border-bottom: none; background: none;" placeholder="________"> | Realizácia: SPEKTRA INSTALL, Rajec
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    function previewImage(event) {
        const reader = new FileReader();
        reader.onload = function() {
            const output = document.getElementById('photoPreview');
            const placeholder = document.getElementById('photoPlaceholder');
            output.src = reader.result;
            output.style.display = 'block';
            placeholder.style.display = 'none';
        }
        reader.readAsDataURL(event.target.files[0]);
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
